			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Moses and Aaron took these men whose names had been specified,",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>and they called the whole community together on the first day of the second month.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-3623AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-3623AP\"></sup> The people registered their ancestry<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-3623AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-3623AQ\"></sup> by their clans and families,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-3623AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-3623AR\"></sup> and the men twenty years old or more<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-3623AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-3623AS\"></sup> were listed by name, one by one,",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>as the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> commanded Moses. And so he counted<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-3624AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-3624AT\"></sup> them in the Desert of Sinai:",
